snippet: The prosecutor general said that Yulia V. Tymoshenko, jailed since 2011, and another former prime minister paid $2.8 million to have a member of Parliament killed.
abstract: Government of Ukraine's Pres Viktor F Yanukovich says it plans to bring murder charges against his political rival, jailed former prime minister Yulia V Tymoshenko, in connection with the 1996 assassination of member of Parliament.
lead_paragraph: The prosecutor general said that Yulia V. Tymoshenko, jailed since 2011, and another former prime minister paid $2.8 million to have a member of Parliament killed.

headline.seo: Ukraine Government to Charge Ex-Premier With Murder
